==John Coate and The Farm==


"Counterculture origins of cyberculture, Part 1: John Coate and The Farm

John Coate, who was instrumental in the early success of the “Whole Earth Lectronic Link,” talks to Howard Rheingold’s class about The Farm—a 1960s commune that influenced the development of the WELL’s virtual community. The first of several parts."
